  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Clinical diagnosis of Hepatocellular carcinoma due to Chronic Hepatitis C Virus
             Infection.

          -  Must be treated with curative treatment for primary tumor using either surgical
             resection or radiofrequency ablation therapy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  No recurrence of hepatocellular carcinoma 3 months after the primary treatment

          -  Renal dysfunction
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
